name: Blue Dots Folded Wallet
description:
Just the basics.

Keep it simple. 



Cut, tooled, and stitched by hand with grey suede pockets.


This wee wallet is perfect for an ID, a few cards and some folded cash. Or use it to hold your fancy business cards.

name: Om Adjustable headband
description:
The sound the universe vibrates to. 

Wear it as a reminder to connect with the world, with yourself, your community. 



This headband is made up of a leather band, on which slides a disk that I've tooled the Om symbol on. Put it on your lovely head, placing the band where you want it and then slide the Om circle in place. With an elastic back strap and a slide to get the right fit, this reminder is fully adjustable! 

Will fit most heads, from 16 - 22 inches around.



Please take this headband off before practicing hot yoga, it has been sealed to protect it from most dirt and the occasional drizzle, but should not go swimming.


Namaste

name: Super Cuff
description:
When you need a little extra power, this cuff will help remind you how awesome and bad-ass you are! Wear it with your head held high.

I designed this cuff with super heroes on the brain, hand cut and stained it to a pretty goldenrod yellow. Perfect for adding that extra pop of color we all need!

Will fit up to a 7" wrist


I will be happy to make this in different colors and sizes, just shoot me a message and we can get started on your custom cuff.

name: Lavender Mandala Cuff
description:
A mediation in stitching.
Hand-pierced leather.
Periwinkle.
Pink.

A quietly bold statement. 




Hand-cut, sealed natural leather embroidered happily with cotton threads. 

This asymmetrical cuff will comfortably fit a wrist 6.5" around or smaller.
